{"word":"γωνία","slug":"γωνία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>γωνία, ας, ἡ</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:γόνυ\">γόνυ</a></el>] <b><i>corner,</i></b> of a street <b><a href='B:470 6:5'>Mt 6:5</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ par.\">par.</a>; of a building <b>21:42; <a href='B:480 12:10'>Mk 12:10</a>; <a href='B:510 4:11'>Ac 4:11</a>; <a href='B:670 2:7'>1 Pt 2:7</a>;</b> of earth’s cardinal points <b><a href='B:730 7:1'>Rv 7:1</a>; <a href='B:730 20:8'>20:8</a>.—</b><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐν\">ἐν</a> γωνίᾳ of <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> done <i>in a corner i.e.</i> in a ‘secluded spot’ = <i>surreptitiously</i> <b><a href='B:510 26:26'>Ac 26:26</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:Γώγ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:Δαβιδ\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}